+/**
+ * ============================================================================
+ * GUIDED TOUR STORE TESTS (Day 36)
+ * ============================================================================
+ *
+ * Tests for guidedTourStore covering:
+ * - State initialization
+ * - Step transitions (start, next, prev, skip, complete)
